title: pipe
description: A function from an imported library.

proc.description: The main process executing code that created the named pipe.

host.description: The host running the process that created the named pipe. Typically the same host referenced in :proc, if present.

exe.description: The specific file containing code that created the named pipe. May or may not be the same :exe specified in :proc, if present.

time.description: The time the named pipe was created.
